## Pair WhatsApp
Visit `https://your-app.onrender.com` > Enter number > Get 8-digit code > Link in WhatsApp

## Commands: 76 Total
Use `.menu` to see all. Categories: General, Group, Owner, Downloader, Fun, AI, Tools

## Warning
Bots violate WhatsApp ToS. Use throwaway numbers. For education only.
